title: Aequs IPO Day 3: Issue sees strong GMP and 11x subscription; should you apply?
description: Aequs’ Rs 921-crore IPO, priced at Rs 118–124, is open from December 3–5, 2025, with listing expected on December 10. The precision engineering firm, which reported higher losses in FY25, has strong OEM partnerships and a vertically integrated model. Analysts…
content: Belagavi-based precision engineering and manufacturing firm Aequs Limited has entered the third and final day of its IPO subscription. By the end of Day 2, the issue received an overwhelming response… [+4035 chars]
